{"finish_reason": "stop", "text": "{
  "action": "keep",
  "confidence": 1.0,
  "criterion": "The assigned card (Real Time Monitoring Heatmap) is the ONLY card in the slot's footprint that renders a 'grouped heatmap visually contrasting instantaneous power states of all feeders', which is the exact analytical story angle. The swap candidates (Source Transfer, Output Load, Energy Flow) serve different analytical intents (Investigation/Transfer Score, Efficiency/Sankey) and do not match the 'live cross-feeder monitoring' snapshot angle.",
  "morphs": {
    "heatmap.title": "Real Time Monitoring (Feeder Heatmap)",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[0].label": "Incomers",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[1].label": "UPS Feeders",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[2].label": "BPDB",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[3].label": "HHF Reactive",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[0].feeders[0].label": "Solar Incomer-1",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[0].feeders[1].label": "Solar Incomer-2",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[1].feeders[0].label": "UPS-01 CL:600KVA",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[1].feeders[1].label": "UPS-02 CL:600KVA",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[1].feeders[2].label": "UPS-03 CL:600KVA",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[1].feeders[3].label": "UPS-04 CL:600KVA",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[1].feeders[4].label": "UPS-05 CL:600KVA",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[1].feeders[5].label": "UPS-06 CL:600KVA",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[2].feeders[0].label": "BPDB-01 Lam-01&02",
    "heatmap.history[0].sections[2].feeders[1].label": "BPDB-02 Lam-03&04",
    "heatmap.selectedSampleIndex": 11
  },
  "data_instructions": {
    "payload_shape": "heatmap",
    "orientation": "entity",
    "entity_dim": "feeder",
    "selection_dim": "metric",
    "selection_role": "produces",
    "binding": {
      "asset_id": "PCC-Panel-1",
      "table": "pcc_panel_1_feedbacks",
      "ts_col": "timestamp",
      "panel_id": null,
      "nameplate_scope": "default"
    },
    "window": {
      "lookback": "24h",
      "sampling": "2s",
      "time_mode": "none"
    },
    "fetch": {
      "endpoint": "real-time-monitoring",
      "window_seconds": 30,
      "interval_seconds": 2,
      "sample_count": 12,
      "range": null,
      "start": null,
      "end": null,
      "sampling": null,
      "metrics": [
        "kw",
        "kvar",
        "pf",
        "voltage",
        "current",
        "iUnbalance"
      ],
      "selection": null
    },
    "fields": [],
    "roster": [
      {
        "slot": "heatmap.history",
        "scope": "members",
        "sample": {
          "label": {
            "b": "ts_label",
            "fmt": "HH:MM:SS"
          }
        },
        "element": {
          "id": {
            "a": "name",
            "b": "slug"
          },
          "kw": {
            "b": "col",
            "c": "active_power_total_kw",
            "q": "power",
            "r": 2
          },
          "pf": {
            "b": "prefer_abs",
            "r": 3,
            "cs": [
              "kpi_true_pf",
              "power_factor_total"
            ]
          },
          "kva": {
            "b": "col",
            "c": "apparent_power_total_kva",
            "q": "power",
            "r": 2
          },
          "kvar": {
            "b": "col",
            "c": "reactive_power_total_kvar",
            "r": 2,
            "keep_sign": true
          },
          "label": {
            "a": "name",
            "b": "attr"
          },
          "current": {
            "b": "col",
            "c": "current_avg",
            "r": 1
          },
          "loadPct": {
            "b": "null",
            "why": "no rated_kva on gic_*"
          },
          "voltage": {
            "b": "col",
            "c": "voltage_ll_avg",
            "r": 1
          },
          "iUnbalance": {
            "b": "col",
            "c": "current_unbalance_pct",
            "r": 2
          },
          "shortLabel": {
            "a": "name",
            "b": "attr"
          }
        },
        "replace": "wholesale",
        "section": {
          "id": "slug_of_group",
          "label": "title_of_group"
        },
        "group_by": "section_defs",
        "match_by": [
          "type",
          "load_group",
          "name_prefix"
        ],
        "unmatched": {
          "id": "slug_of_load_group",
          "note": "members matching no section_def group into a derived section labeled from their load_group; deriveRosterFromHistory renders any section id — group, never drop",
          "label": "load_group",
          "policy": "derived_section"
        },
        "role_filter": "all",
        "section_agg": {
          "totalKw": {
            "r": 2,
            "of": "kw",
            "agg": "sum_magnitude"
          },
          "totalKva": {
            "r": 2,
            "of": "kva",
            "agg": "sum_magnitude"
          },
          "totalKvar": {
            "r": 2,
            "of": "kvar",
            "agg": "sum_magnitude"
          }
        },
        "elements_key": "feeders",
        "section_defs": [
          {
            "id": "incomers",
            "label": "Incomers",
            "roles": [
              "incoming"
            ],
            "types": [
              "incomer",
              "solar-incomer"
            ],
            "load_groups": [
              "incomer",
              "solar"
            ],
            "name_prefixes": [
              "incomer-",
              "solar-incomer-"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "ups",
            "label": "UPS Feeders",
            "types": [
              "ups"
            ],
            "load_groups": [
              "ups"
            ],
            "name_prefixes": [
              "ups-"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "bpdb",
            "label": "BPDB",
            "types": [
              "bpdb"
            ],
            "load_groups": [
              "bpdb"
            ],
            "name_prefixes": [
              "bpdb-"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "hhf",
            "label": "HHF Reactive",
            "types": [
              "hhf"
            ],
            "load_groups": [
              "hhf"
            ],
            "name_prefixes": [
              "hhf-"
            ]
          }
        ],
        "incomers_rule": "role='incoming' members MUST appear in the incomers section — never excluded from heatmap.history (PCC-4 defect 2026-07-03: _reporting_pairs dropped them)",
        "reporting_only": false,
        "incomers_included": true,
        "empty_members_rule": "zero-row members are KEPT as blank rows (per-LEAF degradation, 2026-07-03 sweep fix): a dark meter is a real entity with honest-null readings, exactly like the kept blank incomers; dropping it hid the whole GIC-05 section. Coverage stays the honest telemetry."
      },
      {
        "v": 0,
        "mode": "const",
        "slot": "heatmap.selectedSampleIndex"
      }
    ],
    "coverage_attach": "widgets._coverage",
    "_honest_blanked": [
      "heatmap.history[0].sections[0].feeders[0].kw: Solar Incomer-1 has_data=N (no live power data)",
      "heatmap.history[0].sections[0].feeders[1].kw: Solar Incomer-2 has_data=N (no live power data)",
      "heatmap.history[0].sections[1].feeders[4].kw: UPS-05 CL:600KVA has_data=N (no live power data)",
      "heatmap.history[0].sections[1].feeders[5].kw: UPS-06 CL:600KVA has_data=N (no live power data)",
      "heatmap.history[0].sections[2].feeders[0].kw: BPDB-01 Lam-01&02 has_data=Y but no active_power_total_kw column in its specific table schema (using panel aggregate fallback or blank if unavailable)",
      "heatmap.history[0].sections[2].feeders[1].kw: BPDB-02 Lam-03&04 has_data=Y but no active_power_total_kw column in its specific table schema (using panel aggregate fallback or blank if unavailable)"
    ],
    "data_note": "Roster card: data rides data_instructions.roster. Panel members with has_data=N (Solar Incomers, UPS-05, UPS-06) are kept as blank rows per empty_members_rule. BPDB members have live data but their specific tables may not expose active_power_total_kw directly; the panel aggregate renderer will attempt to fill from available member data or leave blank if the column is strictly absent from the member's schema. The 'loadPct' slot is honest-blanked because the asset's nameplate rated_kva is unknown ('—'), making the denominator for load percentage unavailable (R10/R2)."
  }
}", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 2542, "prompt_tokens": 16985, "prompt_tokens_details": null, "total_tokens": 19527}}

